title: White Dragon Duke: Pendragon
description: White Dragon Duke: Pendragon Manhwa White Dragon Duke: Pendragon is a Manhwa/Manhua/Manga ( English Versoin). Action series, english chapters have been translated and you can read them here. You are reading all chapters on fastest updating our site. Raven Valt, the second son of a lowly nobleman, had been branded as a traitor. With the promise of a pardon, he was sent to fight monsters with the worst unit in the world, the “Rakshasa” Corps. Raven survived ten years in a place where most only lasted one. One day before his pardon, he was on his final mission on the battlefield alongside Eren Pendragon, heir to the Pendragon Duchy… when everything crumbled before his very eyes.
